{"tid":1257741,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"議題：立法會投票問題討論區","createTime":"2019-06-25T17:22:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-25T17:49:23.000Z","uid":197235,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"892c7c9b1324d0d5dd766c83d151fd7f6e087f2e","tid":1257741,"uid":197235,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-25T17:22:03.000Z","msg":"背景：朱凱廸話24個功能組別議員會投反對票，令議案好大機會失敗。<br />\n<br />\n擔憂：過多人於立法會，會大機會發出黃色警示，開唔到會<br />\n<br />\n目的：令會議成功開到，同時減少人投反對票嘅方法<br />\n<br />\n個人建議：唔好太多人去立法會，了解一下邊24個功能組別議員會反對，當見到目標搵約10個人一直同佢傾計，例如問佢哋專長既野，或者唔小心倒瀉水落去佢個身到。但一定要避免導致唔夠議員出席，導致流會，所以要集中24個功能組別議員。（放田少一條生路）<br />\n<br />\n如果有意見請提出，覺得我膠都可以屌，最重要有更多聲音<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">咩意見都好，唔好搞到流會同有警示</span></span>"},{"pid":"d5d5e933b60a04736132f2d340bcb191cba93ac2","tid":1257741,"uid":197235,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-25T17:22:32.000Z","msg":"自己諗，唔好話等議會處理，你咁講代表你無睇新聞"},{"pid":"5e65c0a2a26098a87bfe9066bcdbe11cadf39869","tid":1257741,"uid":197235,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-25T17:22:44.000Z","msg":"交流非分化"},{"pid":"4fcdd9ea98b864b52ab0b0836348f1fa022008d6","tid":1257741,"uid":197235,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-25T17:23:07.000Z","msg":"提咗你地要面對，唔好話無人講"},{"pid":"5b28f8d728354fdd609fde3b43987fda1a344c53","tid":1257741,"uid":197235,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-25T17:23:27.000Z","msg":"唔推就算數"},{"pid":"a672dabee47c3adcce9de25f1f32a7cd662f6156","tid":1257741,"uid":4458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-25T17:40:35.000Z","msg":"大家俾d意見<br />\n可能聽日要早起身出去 <br />\n無人係度傾 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d4305623b457f6f6e7edd8fcb625327d94e19e70","tid":1257741,"uid":197235,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a672dabee47c3adcce9de25f1f32a7cd662f6156